# K6 Stratos — Core Standards

Stack: **Next.js 16** frontend, **Go** REST backend, **Kubernetes** + **InfluxDB**.

## Scoped rules

| Area | Rule file | When it applies |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend UI text | `i18n-multilingual.mdc` | All user-visible strings in en/fr/he/zh |
| Backend HA | `backend-ha-leader-election.mdc` | DB workers, scheduler, multi-replica deploy |

## Skills

- API tokens, RBAC, relaunch pipeline → `.cursor/skills/k6-stratum-portal-integrator/SKILL.md`
- Dashboard observability → `.cursor/skills/k6-bedrock-dashboard/SKILL.md`
- OpenSpec change workflow → `.cursor/skills/openspec-*/SKILL.md`

## Key paths

- Translations: `frontend/src/components/PreferencesContext.tsx`
- Backend entry: `backend/cmd/api/main.go`
- Scheduler: `backend/internal/server/scheduler.go`
- K8s deploy: `k8s-deployment.yaml`
